# Ship Pipeline — CI→UAT→PROD

## Pipeline Flow

```
qge_analyze_shape → Build → qge_pre_ci_gate → trigger_ci_pipeline
  → qge_pre_uat_gate → promote_to_uat → qge_pre_prod_gate
  → promote_to_prod → check_post_deploy_health
```

## Steps

### 1. Post-Shape Gate
`qge_analyze_shape(requirements_doc, design_doc, chain_id?)` — requirements completeness, design feasibility, domain compliance.

### 2. Pre-CI Gate
`qge_pre_ci_gate(source_id, branch, chain_id?)` — automated, no HITL. Unit tests, lint, secrets.

### 3. Trigger CI
`trigger_ci_pipeline(source_id, branch, issue_key, jenkins_job?)` — trigger Jenkins, comment Jira.

### 4. Pre-UAT Gate
`qge_pre_uat_gate(service, build_number, issue_key)` — **tạo HITL approval** cho Quality Reviewer. Chờ approval trước khi promote.

### 5. Promote UAT
`promote_to_uat(service, build_number, issue_key, jenkins_deploy_job, approval_id)` — cần approval_id.

### 6. Pre-PROD Gate
`qge_pre_prod_gate(service, build_number, issue_key)` — **tạo HITL approval** cho Quality Reviewer + System Operator.

### 7. Promote PROD
`promote_to_prod(service, build_number, issue_key, jenkins_deploy_job, approval_id)` — approval bắt buộc.

### 8. Health Check
`check_post_deploy_health(service, environment, build_number, issue_key)` — PROD rollback cần HITL, CI/UAT auto-rollback.

## Rollback
`rollback(service, environment, to_build_number, issue_key, reason?)` — PROD cần HITL approval.

## Impact Analysis
`ship_impact_analysis(source_id, chain_id, max_depth?)` — intra-chain impact trước khi deploy.

## Gate Summary

| Gate | Automated? | HITL? | Who Approves? |
|------|-----------|-------|---------------|
| Post-Shape | AI 80% | Human review | Intent Owner + Solution Reviewer |
| Pre-CI | 100% | No | — |
| Pre-UAT | AI 90% | Yes | Quality Reviewer |
| Pre-PROD | AI 80% | Yes | Quality Reviewer + System Operator |
| Post-Deploy | AI detect | PROD rollback only | System Operator |
